      "content": "fair enough. so if the data shows it doesn't really help the bottom 50% that much, wouldn't that basically mean the tax reform is just a way to widen the gap? like, if the \"growth\" argument is mostly just theory and not reality, isn't it more accurate to say the bill is designed specifically to benefit the wealthy?",
